hair is the\npatron 15.\n","linknr":113,"url":"Cruz_e_Souza","recorded":1374521280,"links":["/w/index.php?title=Jo%C3%A3o_da_Cruz_e_Sousa&action=edit","/w/index.php?title=Jo%C3%A3o_da_Cruz_e_Sousa&action=edit","//bits.wikimedia.org/favicon/wikipedia.ico","/w/opensearch_desc.php","//en.wikipedia.org/w/api.php?action=rsd","//creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/","/w/index.php?title=Special:RecentChanges&feed=atom","/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o_da_Cruz_e_Sousa","//bits.wikimedia.org/en.wikipedia.org/load.php?debug=false&lang=en&modules=ext.gadget.DRN-wizard%2CReferenceTooltips%2Ccharinsert%2Cteahouse%7Cext.rtlcite%2Cwikihiero%7Cext.uls.nojs%7Cmediawiki.legacy.commonPrint%2Cshared%7Cmw.PopUpMediaTransform%7Cskins.vector&only=styles&skin=vector&*","//bits.wikimedia.org/en.wikipedia.org/load.php?debug=false&lang=en&modules=site&only=styles&skin=vector&*","//bits.wikimedia.org/en.wikipedia.org/load.php?debug=false&lang=en&modules=startup&only=scripts&skin=vector&*","//bits.wikimedia.org/geoiplookup","//meta.wikimedia.org","/w/index.php?title=Cruz_e_Souza&redirect=no","#mw-navigation","#p-search","/wiki/File:Cruz_e_Sousa.jpg","//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/35/Cruz_e_Sousa.jpg/235px-Cruz_e_Sousa.jpg","/wiki/File:Cruz_e_Sousa.jpg","//bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.22wmf10/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png","/wiki/Florian%C3%B3polis","/wiki/Symbolism_(arts)","/wiki/Santa_Catarina_(state)","/wiki/Brazil","/wiki/Afro-Brazilian","/wiki/Marshal_(Brazil)","/wiki/Fritz_M%C3%BCller","#A_Forerunner_of_Negritude","#Books","#References","#External_links","/w/index.php?title=Jo%C3%A3o_da_Cruz_e_Sousa&action=edit&section=1","/wiki/Jerome_Arnold","/wiki/Jerome_Arnold","/w/index.php?title=Jo%C3%A3o_da_Cruz_e_Sousa&action=edit&section=2","/w/index.php?title=Jo%C3%A3o_da_Cruz_e_Sousa&action=edit&section=3","/w/index.php?title=Jo%C3%A3o_da_Cruz_e_Sousa&action=edit&section=4","//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4c/Wikisource-logo.svg/38px-Wikisource-logo.svg.png","/wiki/W